libpinyin
------------------------------------------
The libpinyin project aims to provide the algorithms core for intelligent
sentence-based Chinese pinyin input methods.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-1.7.17-1
  gettext-0.18.1.1-2
  libdb4.8-4.8.30-1
  libgcc1-4.5.3-3
  libglib2.0-devel-2.32.4-1
  libglib2.0_0-2.32.4-1
  libiconv-1.14-2
  libpcre-devel-8.31-1
  libstdc++6-4.5.3-3
  libstdc++6-devel-4.5.3-3

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-10-1
  automake-7-1
  binutils-2.22.51-2
  cygport-0.11.2-1
  gawk-4.0.1-1
  gcc4-core-4.5.3-3
  gcc4-g++-4.5.3-3
  libtool-2.4-1
  make-3.82.90-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/libpinyin/libpinyin

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/downloads/libpinyin/libpinyin/libpinyin-0.8.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack libpinyin-0.8.0-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./libpinyin-0.8.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libpinyin-0.8.0-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libpinyin-0.8.0-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libpinyin2-0.8.0-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libpinyin-devel-0.8.0-X.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libpinyin)
  /usr/bin/gen_binary_files.exe
  /usr/bin/gen_unigram.exe
  /usr/bin/import_interpolation.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libpinyin.README
  /usr/share/doc/libpinyin/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/libpinyin/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/libpinyin/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/libpinyin/README
  /usr/share/man/man1/gen_binary_files.1.gz
  /usr/share/man/man1/gen_unigram.1.gz
  /usr/share/man/man1/import_interpolation.1.gz
  /usr/share/man/man1/libpinyin.1.gz

(libpinyin2)
  /usr/bin/cygpinyin-2.dll
  /usr/share/libpinyin/data/bigram.db
  /usr/share/libpinyin/data/gb_char.bin
  /usr/share/libpinyin/data/gbk_char.bin
  /usr/share/libpinyin/data/phrase_index.bin
  /usr/share/libpinyin/data/pinyin_index.bin

(libpinyin-devel)
  /usr/include/libpinyin-0.8.0/chewing_enum.h
  /usr/include/libpinyin-0.8.0/chewing_key.h
  /usr/include/libpinyin-0.8.0/novel_types.h
  /usr/include/libpinyin-0.8.0/pinyin.h
  /usr/include/libpinyin-0.8.0/pinyin_custom2.h
  /usr/lib/libpinyin.dll.a
  /usr/lib/libpinyin.la
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libpinyin.pc

